com.hazelcast.spi.impl.operationparker.impl

Class WaitSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.spi.impl.operationparker.impl.WaitSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LiveOperationsTracker, Iterable<com.hazelcast.spi.impl.operationparker.impl.WaitSetEntry>

    public class WaitSet
extends Object
implements LiveOperationsTracker, Iterable<com.hazelcast.spi.impl.operationparker.impl.WaitSetEntry>
    The WaitSet is a effectively a set of operations waiting for some condition. For example it could be a set of lock-operations that are waiting for a lock to come available.
